
Create an API with UI to Signup and Login functionality.
After login user will be able to upload the documents.
- Profile Photo
- Aadhar Card
- Pan Card
- Voter ID Proof
- Marksheet.
After uploading save all the documents in database in base64 or blob format. 
Prepare a functionality to download all the documents in zip format based on current user. 
After extract zip the documents should be available as same they are uploaded. 
The documents should be in png, pdf, jpg, jpeg, ppt, pptx, doc, docx.
